room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
room_address: 830 Union Street Suite 101 New Orleans, LA 70112
room_description: The Vampire Lestat has traveled to his hiding place to hibernate and hide his family’s riches. He has been resting for quite some time. Your team of vampire hunters is tasked with finding the vampire’s lair, navigating the darkness, and killing Lestat with a stake through the heart before he wakes.
